 Kugayama - Machida - Miyanosaka - Nakano - Nerima - Nishi-Ogikubo - Ogikubo - Sangenjaya - Sasazuka - Setagaya - Shimokitazawa - Tachikawa - Tama - Umegaoka - Yoga - Ōme 🏘 Yokohama and Kanagawa - Bashamichi - Chigasaki - Ebina - Enoshima - Fujisawa - Hadano - Hakone - Hiratsuka - Kamakura - Kanagawa - Kawasaki - Matsuda - Minami-Ashigara - Minatomirai - Miura - Motomachi - Odawara - Sagamihara - Yamashita - Yokohama - Yokosuka - Zama - Zushi 🏘 Ibaraki\nClear Submit\nCheapo Events Monthly Article: [May 2026: 8 Events Not To Miss in Tokyo](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/tokyo-events-may/)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/07/crouching-tiger-hidden-sumo-362x193.jpg) May 10 ~ May 24 Featured ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/may-grand-sumo-tournament/ \"May Grand Sumo Tournament\")\n###  [ May Grand Sumo Tournament ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/may-grand-sumo-tournament/ \"May Grand Sumo Tournament\")\nThe third of Japan's six annual sumo tournaments. \n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/may-grand-sumo-tournament/)\n[Sport](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/sport-2)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/east-tokyo/ryogoku/)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2026/02/azuma25_okonomi_B044-362x193.jpg) May 22 ~ May 25 Featured ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/azuma-odori/ \"Azuma Odori — Tokyo Geisha Performance\")\n###  [ Azuma Odori — Tokyo Geisha Performance ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/azuma-odori/ \"Azuma Odori — Tokyo Geisha Performance\")\nOne of the best — and most authentic — ways to see geisha in Tokyo.\n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/azuma-odori/)\n[Dance](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/dance)\n[Festival](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/festival)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/central-tokyo/ginza/)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2014/07/adachi-fireworks-GettyImages-582286736-362x193.jpg) Sat, May 30 Featured ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/adachi-fireworks-festival-2/ \"Adachi Fireworks Festival 2026\")\n###  [ Adachi Fireworks Festival 2026 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/adachi-fireworks-festival-2/ \"Adachi Fireworks Festival 2026\")\nThe annual Adachi Fireworks Festival is held along the Arakawa River.\n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/adachi-fireworks-festival-2/)\n7:20pm – 8:20pm\n[Fireworks](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/fireworks)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/north-tokyo/kitasenju/)\n  * You can list your Tokyo events on Tokyo Cheapo, [click here](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-listing/) to send us details\n  * [ ![stand up comedian in tokyo](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/08/Comedy-BJ-Fox-362x193.jpg) Fri, May 22 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/weekend-comedy-tcb/ \"Weekend Comedy at TCB\")\n###  [ Weekend Comedy at TCB ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/weekend-comedy-tcb/ \"Weekend Comedy at TCB\")\n★ Staff recommendation \nTokyo Comedy Bar offers some of the best chuckles in Tokyo.\n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/weekend-comedy-tcb/)\n7:30pm – 10:00pm\n[Comedy](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/comedy)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/central-tokyo/shibuya-2/)\n  * [ ![Okonomiyaki cooking party WeLearn](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2026/04/AdobeStock_219886796-362x193.jpeg) Fri, May 22 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/okonomiyaki-cooking-party-in-akihabara/ \"Okonomiyaki Cooking Party in Akihabara\")\n###  [ Okonomiyaki Cooking Party in Akihabara ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/okonomiyaki-cooking-party-in-akihabara/ \"Okonomiyaki Cooking Party in Akihabara\")\nMake okonomiyaki and new friends at this social event in Akihabara. \n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/okonomiyaki-cooking-party-in-akihabara/)\n6:00pm – 8:00pm\n[Food](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/food)\n[Living](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/living)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/central-tokyo/akihabara-central-tokyo/)\n  * [ ![event sub](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2026/04/CRAFTROVERTS_FEST-362x193.jpg) Fri, May 22 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/craftroverts-fest/ \"Craftroverts’ Fest\")\n###  [ Craftroverts’ Fest ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/craftroverts-fest/ \"Craftroverts’ Fest\")\nCraftroverts’ Fest is a small, creative pop-up event in Shinjuku.\n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/craftroverts-fest/)\n2:00pm – 9:00pm\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/central-tokyo/shinjuku/)\n  * ## Get Tokyo's best events in your inbox every week\nSubscribe \n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/11/microphone-karaoke_loveshiba_GettyImages-1460707686-362x193.jpg) Sat, May 23 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/karaoke-welearn-community-in-akihabara/ \"Karaoke @WeLearn Community in Akihabara\")\n###  [ Karaoke @WeLearn Community in Akihabara ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/karaoke-welearn-community-in-akihabara/ \"Karaoke @WeLearn Community in Akihabara\")\nJoin a karaoke party at WeLearn in Akihabara. \n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/karaoke-welearn-community-in-akihabara/)\n[Living](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/living)\n[Music](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/music-2)\n[Party](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/party)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/central-tokyo/akihabara-central-tokyo/)\n  * [ ![Shimokitazawa](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/GettyImages-1460861764-362x193.jpg) Sat, May 23 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/shimokitazawa-sound-cruising/ \"Shimokitazawa Sound Cruising\")\n###  [ Shimokitazawa Sound Cruising ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/shimokitazawa-sound-cruising/ \"Shimokitazawa Sound Cruising\")\nCatch over 150 artists performing in 17 venues around Shimokita. \n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/shimokitazawa-sound-cruising/)\n12:30pm\n[Music](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/music-2)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/west-tokyo/shimokitazawa-2/)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/05/main-1-362x193.jpg) Sat, May 23 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/star-island-odaiba-fireworks-festival/ \"Star Island Odaiba Fireworks Festival\")\n###  [ Star Island Odaiba Fireworks Festival ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/star-island-odaiba-fireworks-festival/ \"Star Island Odaiba Fireworks Festival\")\nExperience fireworks like never before at the Star Island Odaiba Fireworks Festival taking place this June. \n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/star-island-odaiba-fireworks-festival/)\n4:30pm – 9:00pm\n[Fireworks](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/fireworks)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/central-tokyo/odaiba/)\n  * [ ![Goods on display at a flea market stall, a winter event in Tokyo.](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/09/GettyImages-2190620219-362x193.jpg) May 22 ~ May 23 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/tennoz-harbor-market/20260522/ \"Tennoz Harbor Market\")\n###  [ Tennoz Harbor Market ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/tennoz-harbor-market/20260522/ \"Tennoz Harbor Market\")\nIf you’re after something low-key but creative, this one’s an easy addition to your calendar.\n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/tennoz-harbor-market/20260522/)\n[Market](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/market)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/central-tokyo/odaiba/)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/08/ohi-racecourse-fleamarket-outdoors-362x193.jpg) May 22 ~ May 23 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/ohi-racecourse-flea-market/20260522/ \"Ohi Racecourse Flea Market\")\n###  [ Ohi Racecourse Flea Market ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/ohi-racecourse-flea-market/20260522/ \"Ohi Racecourse Flea Market\")\nOne of the biggest flea markets in Tokyo, there's almost nothing you won't be able to find amongst the rows of stalls and tarps. Feel free to haggle while you hunt, it's all part of the appeal […](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/ohi-racecourse-flea-market/)\n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/ohi-racecourse-flea-market/20260522/)\n9:00am – 2:30pm\n[Market](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/market)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/south-tokyo/oimachi/) [](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/south-tokyo/oomori/)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/09/meat-festival-GettyImages-531464020-362x193.jpeg) May 23 ~ May 24 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/nikuon/ \"Nikuon\")\n###  [ Nikuon ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/nikuon/ \"Nikuon\")\nTry out the meats and the beats.\n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/nikuon/)\n11:00am – 7:00pm\n[Food](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/food)\n[Music](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/music-2)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/east-tokyo/kinshicho/)\n  * [ ![live concert audience](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/09/GettyImages-494388654-362x193.jpg) May 23 ~ May 24 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/greenroom-festival/ \"Greenroom Festival\")\n###  [ Greenroom Festival ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/greenroom-festival/ \"Greenroom Festival\")\nYokohama’s much-loved Green Room Festival is back again this year. \n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/greenroom-festival/)\n[Festival](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/festival)\n[Music](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/music-2)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/yokohama-and-kanagawa/yokohama/)\n  * [ ![A group of people standing while they eat a tasty dish from a Fall food festival](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2026/04/GettyImages-1456220672-362x193.jpg) May 22 ~ May 24 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/tennoz-canal-fes-spring/ \"Tennoz Canal Fes \\(Spring\\)\")\n###  [ Tennoz Canal Fes (Spring) ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/tennoz-canal-fes-spring/ \"Tennoz Canal Fes \\(Spring\\)\")\nThis family-friendly handmade market features crafts, vintage goods, and local food vendors along the waterfront.\n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/tennoz-canal-fes-spring/)\n[Food](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/food)\n[Market](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/market)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/south-tokyo/shinagawa/)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2026/04/Main_Continuous-Life-and-Death-at-the-Now-of-Deep-Time_yorovalley-362x193.jpg) Apr 17 ~ May 24 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/teamlab-yoro-valley/ \"teamLab Yoro Valley\")\n###  [ teamLab Yoro Valley ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/teamlab-yoro-valley/ \"teamLab Yoro Valley\")\nWalk through illuminated hiking paths where artworks respond to your presence.\n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/teamlab-yoro-valley/)\n[Art](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/art)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/chiba/)\n  * [ ![Flea market Japan Tokyo](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/08/Flea-market-Japan-iStock-530003716-akiyoko-362x193.jpg) Sun, May 24 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/tokyo-romantic-flea-market/ \"Tokyo Romantic Flea Market\")\n###  [ Tokyo Romantic Flea Market ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/tokyo-romantic-flea-market/ \"Tokyo Romantic Flea Market\")\nEnjoy a sweet stroll around this antique Tokyo Flea Market. \n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/tokyo-romantic-flea-market/)\n10:00am – 4:00pm\n[Market](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/market)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/east-tokyo/ariake/) [](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/east-tokyo/oshiage/) [](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/central-tokyo/shibuya-2/)\n  * [ ![Tokyo Night Market](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/08/Tokyo-Night-Market-362x193.jpg) May 20 ~ May 24 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/tokyo-night-market/ \"Tokyo Night Market\")\n###  [ Tokyo Night Market ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/tokyo-night-market/ \"Tokyo Night Market\")\nA market under the stars awaits at the Tokyo Night Market.\n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/tokyo-night-market/)\n[Market](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/market)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/central-tokyo/yoyogi/)\n  * [ ![tokyo antique market](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2014/12/Oedo-Antique-Market-CF-362x193.jpg) Sun, May 24 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/oedo-antique-market/ \"The Oedo Antique Market\")\n###  [ The Oedo Antique Market ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/oedo-antique-market/ \"The Oedo Antique Market\")\nThe Oedo Antique Market is the largest outdoor antique market in Japan.\n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/oedo-antique-market/)\n9:00am – 4:00pm\n[Market](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/market)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/central-tokyo/yurakucho/)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/11/laos-festival-yoyogi-iStock-1152197484-362x193.jpg) May 23 ~ May 24 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/laos-festival/ \"Laos Festival 2026\")\n###  [ Laos Festival 2026 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/laos-festival/ \"Laos Festival 2026\")\nThe Laos Festival is filled with Laotian dancing, music, workshops, and, best of all, food.\n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/laos-festival/)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/central-tokyo/shibuya-2/)\n  * [ ![happy spring festa 2025](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/main-4-362x193.jpg) Apr 4 ~ May 24 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/happy-spring-festa/ \"Happy Spring Festa at Musashi Kyūryō Park\")\n###  [ Happy Spring Festa at Musashi Kyūryō Park ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/happy-spring-festa/ \"Happy Spring Festa at Musashi Kyūryō Park\")\nSpring has sprung at Musashino National Government Park, where 700,000 Iceland poppies burst into life alongside fields of nemophila and lupines. \n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/happy-spring-festa/)\n9:30am – 4:00pm\n[Nature](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/nature)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/saitama/)\n  * [ ![](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/11/beer-mount-takao-362x193.jpeg) Mar 19 ~ May 24 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/takao-beer-mount-spring/ \"Takao Beer Mount Spring Edition\")\n###  [ Takao Beer Mount Spring Edition ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/takao-beer-mount-spring/ \"Takao Beer Mount Spring Edition\")\nThe ultimate view of Tokyo from the skies awaits at the top of Mt Takao — with food and drinks included.\n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/takao-beer-mount-spring/)\n11:00am – 5:00pm\n[Beer](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/beer)\n[Food](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/food)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/west-tokyo/hachioji/)\n  * [ ![game market spring](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/06/sub1-3-362x193.jpg) May 23 ~ May 24 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/tokyo-game-market-spring/ \"Tokyo Game Market \\(Spring\\)\")\n###  [ Tokyo Game Market (Spring) ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/tokyo-game-market-spring/ \"Tokyo Game Market \\(Spring\\)\")\nInto minimalist abstract strategy games, world-building RPGs, or board games about running a pharmaceutical company? You may want to check this event out.\n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/tokyo-game-market-spring/)\n[Market](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/market)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/chiba/makuhari/)\n  * [ ![tulips in bloom](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/03/iStock-665801426-362x193.jpg) Mar 20 ~ May 24 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/spring-flowers-at-showa-kinen-park/ \"Spring Flowers at Showa Kinen Park\")\n###  [ Spring Flowers at Showa Kinen Park ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/spring-flowers-at-showa-kinen-park/ \"Spring Flowers at Showa Kinen Park\")\nEnjoy a carpet of flowers from around the world at Showa Kinen Park. Stretch your legs as your stroll amongst fields of tulips, poppies, cherry blossoms, and more!\n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/spring-flowers-at-showa-kinen-park/)\n9:30am – 5:00pm\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/west-tokyo/tachikawa-2/)\n  * [ ![Mangaka at work](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/06/Design-Festa-Mangaka-362x193.jpg) May 23 ~ May 24 ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/design-festa-spring/ \"Design Festa Vol. 63: Spring Edition\")\n###  [ Design Festa Vol. 63: Spring Edition ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/design-festa-spring/ \"Design Festa Vol. 63: Spring Edition\")\nGet creative at one of Asia's largest art events. \n[ Read more ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/design-festa-spring/)\n10:00am – 6:00pm\n[Art](https://tokyocheapo.com/event-category/art)\n[](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/east-tokyo/ariake/) [](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/location/central-tokyo/odaiba/)\n\n\n[1](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/)\n[2](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/page/2/)\n[3](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/page/3/)\n[4](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/page/4/)\n[5](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/page/5/)\n[»](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/page/2/)\n## Tokyo's Best Events and Cultural Activities in Your Inbox Every Week\nSubscribe \n### Recommended hotels in Tokyo\n[ More Tokyo Hotels ](https://www.booking.com/city/jp/tokyo.html?aid=386482)\n  * [ ![Hilton Tokyo](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2021/02/Hilton-Tokyo-5-by-CFM-562x421.jpg) ](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=Hilton+Tokyo&address=)\n[Hilton Tokyo](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=Hilton+Tokyo&address=)\n  * [ ![Hotel Rose Garden Shinjuku](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/10/hotel-lobby-562x421.jpeg) from ¥7,000 ](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=Hotel+Rose+Garden+Shinjuku&address=8-1-3+Nishi-Shinjuku%2C+Shinjuku%2C+Tokyo)\n[Hotel Rose Garden Shinjuku](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=Hotel+Rose+Garden+Shinjuku&address=8-1-3+Nishi-Shinjuku%2C+Shinjuku%2C+Tokyo)\n  * [ ![Aloft Tokyo Ginza](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/10/aloft-rooftop-van-562x421.jpg) from ¥24,456 ](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=Aloft+Tokyo+Ginza&address=6-14-3+Ginza+Chuo-ku%2C+Tokyo%2C+Japan%2C+1040061)\n[Aloft Tokyo Ginza](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=Aloft+Tokyo+Ginza&address=6-14-3+Ginza+Chuo-ku%2C+Tokyo%2C+Japan%2C+1040061)\n  * [ ![Marroad International Hotel Narita](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2016/04/42973_15072116360032709971-562x421.jpg) ](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=Marroad+International+Hotel+Narita&address=763-1+Komaino%2C+Narita-City%2C+286-0121)\n[Marroad International Hotel Narita](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=Marroad+International+Hotel+Narita&address=763-1+Komaino%2C+Narita-City%2C+286-0121)\n  * [ ![Shinjuku Kuyakusho-mae Capsule Hotel](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/07/IMG_9660-copy-562x421.jpg) from ¥6,000 ](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=Shinjuku+Kuyakusho-mae+Capsule+Hotel&address=1-2-5+Kabukicho%2C+Shinjuku+Ward%2C+Tokyo)\n[Shinjuku Kuyakusho-mae Capsule Hotel](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=Shinjuku+Kuyakusho-mae+Capsule+Hotel&address=1-2-5+Kabukicho%2C+Shinjuku+Ward%2C+Tokyo)\n  * [ ![FLEXSTAY INN Shinagawa](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/11/FLEXSTAY-INN-Shinagawa-exterior_agoda-562x421.jpg) from ¥6,050 ](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=FLEXSTAY+INN+Shinagawa&address=1-22-19+Kitashinagawa%2C+Shinagawa-ku%2C+Tokyo+140-0001+Japan)\n[FLEXSTAY INN Shinagawa](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=FLEXSTAY+INN+Shinagawa&address=1-22-19+Kitashinagawa%2C+Shinagawa-ku%2C+Tokyo+140-0001+Japan)\n  * [ ![Mustard Hotel Shibuya](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/07/Mustard-Hotel-562x421.jpeg) from ¥9,000 ](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=Mustard+Hotel+Shibuya&address=1+Chome-29-3+Higashi%2C+Shibuya+City%2C+Tokyo+150-0011)\n[Mustard Hotel Shibuya](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=Mustard+Hotel+Shibuya&address=1+Chome-29-3+Higashi%2C+Shibuya+City%2C+Tokyo+150-0011)\n  * [ ![Tokyu Stay Tsukiji](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2016/03/tokyu-stay-tsukiji-562x421.jpg) from ¥7,300 ](http://www.agoda.com/tokyu-stay-tsukiji/hotel/tokyo-jp.html?cid=1551732)\n[Tokyu Stay Tsukiji](http://www.agoda.com/tokyu-stay-tsukiji/hotel/tokyo-jp.html?cid=1551732)\n  * [ ![Shinjuku Kuyakushomae Capsule Hotel](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2017/02/Shinjuku-Kuyakushomae-Capsule-Hotel-1-562x421.jpg) from ¥3,399 ](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=Shinjuku+Kuyakushomae+Capsule+Hotel&address=160-0021+Tokyo+Prefecture%2C+Shinjuku-ku%2C+Kabukich%C5%8D+1-2-5%2C+Japan)\n[Shinjuku Kuyakushomae Capsule Hotel](https://www.stay22.com/allez/wildcard?aid=fasttrainlimited&campaign=tokyocheapo&hotelname=Shinjuku+Kuyakushomae+Capsule+Hotel&address=160-0021+Tokyo+Prefecture%2C+Shinjuku-ku%2C+Kabukich%C5%8D+1-2-5%2C+Japan)\n\n\n[ ![Scroll Up](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/themes/cheapo_theme/assets/icons/arrow-up-solid.svg.gzip) ](https://tokyocheapo.com/events/)\n##### About Tokyo Cheapo\n## About\nWith 500,000 - 800,000 readers each month, Tokyo Cheapo is the site of choice for value hunters who want their yen to go further in Tokyo. We cover all the basics including [things to do in Tokyo](https://tokyocheapo.com/living/101-free-and-cheap-things-to-do-in-tokyo/), how to [get from Narita airport to Tokyo](https://tokyocheapo.com/travel/transport/cheapest-transport-to-and-from-narita-airport/), [which JR rail pass to choose](https://tokyocheapo.com/travel/transport/which-jr-rail-pass-to-choose/), getting a [SIM card](https://tokyocheapo.com/business/internet/prepaid-cheap-japan-sim-card-options/) and [pocket wifi](https://tokyocheapo.com/business/internet/rent-wifi-router-japan/). \nTo find why we started this site, check out the [Tokyo Cheapo Manifesto](https://tokyocheapo.com/living/tokyo-cheapo-manifesto/ \"The Tokyo Cheapo Manifesto\"). For more about the people behind this site, check out the [profiles of the cheapos](https://tokyocheapo.com/cheapos/ \"The Cheapos\"). If you want to contribute, see [our careers page](https://fasttrainltd.com/careers/). For advertising and sponsorship of our Tokyo Cheapo channels, [get in touch here](https://fasttrainltd.com/#contact). \n**Affiliate Links**\nSome of the articles on this site contain affiliate links. If you purchase from or sign up with some companies we link to, we will be compensated. We don't endorse any of the companies we link to but we are selective in terms of the companies that we choose. You should exercise careful judgement with any online purchase. Additionally, the terms of all offers are subject to change without notice. \n**Sponsored Content**\nSponsored posts are clearly labeled with a \"Sponsored\" tag. Additionally, content such as tours and tickets, hotels and apartments are commercial content. \nFor more on the Tokyo Cheapo story, go to our [About Page](https://tokyocheapo.com/about/). \n![endless discovery logo](https://cdn.cheapoguides.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/07/endless-discovery-logo-white.png)\n##### Site Map\n  * Locations\n  * [Akasaka](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/akasaka/)\n  * [Akihabara](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/akihabara-central-tokyo/)\n  * [Asakusa](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/east-tokyo/asakusa/)\n  * [Ginza](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/ginza/)\n  * [Harajuku](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/harajuku/)\n  * [Odaiba](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/odaiba/)\n  * [Omotesandō](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/omotesando/)\n  * [Roppongi](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/roppongi/)\n  * [Shibuya](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/shibuya-2/)\n  * [Shimokitazawa](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/west-tokyo/shimokitazawa-2/)\n  * [Shinjuku](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/central-tokyo/shinjuku/)\n  * [Ueno](https://tokyocheapo.com/locations/east-tokyo/ueno/)\n  * [More](https://tokyocheapo.com/all-locations)\n\n\n  * Categories\n  * [Anime And Gaming](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/anime-and-gaming/)\n  * [Art](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/art/)\n  * [Business](https://tokyocheapo.com/business/)\n  * [Cafés](https://tokyocheapo.com/food-and-drink/cafe/)\n  * [Drinking](https://tokyocheapo.com/food-and-drink/drinking/)\n  *     * [Eating & Drinking](https://tokyocheapo.com/food-and-drink/)\n    * [Education](https://tokyocheapo.com/living/education/)\n    * [Events](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/event-posts/)\n    * [Family](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/family/)\n    * [Fashion](https://tokyocheapo.com/shopping-2/fashion/)\n    * [Financial](https://tokyocheapo.com/business/financial/)\n    * [Getting around](https://tokyocheapo.com/travel/)\n    * [Holidays](https://tokyocheapo.com/travel/holidays/)\n    * [Household](https://tokyocheapo.com/living/household/)\n    * [International Food](https://tokyocheapo.com/food-and-drink/international-food/)\n    * [Internet](https://tokyocheapo.com/business/internet/)\n    * [Japanese Culture And Tradition](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/japanese-culture-and-tradition/)\n    * [Lifestyle](https://tokyocheapo.com/lifestyle/)\n    * [Living](https://tokyocheapo.com/living/)\n    * [Movies, Shows and Theatre](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/movies-theatre/)\n    * [Museums And Exhibitions](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/museums-and-exhibitions/)\n    * [Music and Nightlife](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/music-and-nightlife/)\n    * [Outdoors and Nature](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/outdoors/)\n    * [Places to stay](https://tokyocheapo.com/accommodationcat/)\n    * [Podcast](https://tokyocheapo.com/podcast/)\n    * [Ramen](https://tokyocheapo.com/food-and-drink/ramen/)\n    * [Seasonal Activities](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/seasonal-activities/)\n    * [Shopping](https://tokyocheapo.com/shopping-2/)\n    * [Sightseeing](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/sightseeing/)\n    * [Snow Sports](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/snow-sports/)\n    * [Sporting Activities](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/sport/)\n    * [Sushi](https://tokyocheapo.com/food-and-drink/sushi/)\n    * [Sweets](https://tokyocheapo.com/food-and-drink/sweets/)\n    * [Themeparks and Zoos](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/themeparks-and-zoos/)\n    * [Things to do in Tokyo](https://tokyocheapo.com/entertainment/)\n    * [Transport](https://tokyocheapo.com/travel/transport/)\n\n\n  * About Us\n  * [お問い合わせ](https://tokyocheapo.com/contact-form_ja/)\n  * [Contact Us](https://tokyocheapo.com/contact